data.title: Air Pollution
data.meta_description:
Februay_2022 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. - President Ram Nath Kovind attended the 50th anniversary celebrations of Bangladesh's independence in Dhaka as the only foreign dignitary. 
- Russian President Vladimir Putin visited New Delhi for the 21st India-Russia Annual Summit and both countries signed 28 agreements across various sectors.
- India hosted the third meeting of the India-Central Asia Dialogue between foreign ministers of India and Central Asian countries in New Delhi.
- The WHO approved Covovax, the COVID-19 vaccine produced by Serum Institute of India, as the ninth vaccine approved by the WHO.
